    "created_at": "2023-02-16T19:25:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-02-16T19:25:57Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Apologies @BearCooder for the change there. We had big hopes for integrating Tezos into Truffle, but our initial Proof of Concept showed us that proper support would require a significant amount of effort, since Truffle is quite tightly-coupled with the EVM. Since this project is in a position of juggling priorities with limited labor-power, we had to stop our efforts to make Tezos first-class in our tools.\r\n\r\nPossibly in the future, we'll improve Truffle's architecture to the point where supporting other blockchain computer architectures becomes feasible, but unfortunately that's just not the case today. Hopefully there are alternative tools for Tezos smart contract development that you can use instead of Truffle.\r\n\r\nThanks for understanding.",
